description:
Season: 20
Original Air Date: 9/25/2006

Brooke questions Bridget about why she is not going to Africa. Nick walks in as Bridget tries to explain. Nick asks Brooke to renew their vows. Brooke and Nick renew their vows and Bridget and Felicia watch from the terrace. Felicia tries to convince Bridget to tell Nick about the pregnancy. Bridget agrees and wants to tell her mom the truth. Later, Bridget tells a stunned Nick that she is pregnant with his child. Shane admits to Hector and Phoebe that he does have a criminal record and that he is now trying to get his life together. Later, Shane asks Phoebe out on a date and she accepts. Hector overhears their conversation and is none to pleased.
